title.rendered: BOSS AIR 12V AIR COMPRESSOR TANK COMPLETE

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR 12V AIR COMPRESSOR TANK COMPLETE

Boss Air 12V Air Compressor Tank Complete available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Boss Air’s new all-in-one air source solution with no additional plumbing required. Compressor is mounted into the air tank ready to go.

Includes:

  • Tank 1gallon
  • Pressure Gauge
  • 110-140psi pressure switch
  • Drain tap
  • 1/4″ Tube compression fitting
  • Inbuilt Compressor
  • 12v DC
  • 25% duty cycle@100psi
  • 1.9cfm
  • Max amp draw 20amps
  • Max working pressure 150psi
  • Fill time from 0 to 140psi=88 seconds
  • Dimensions 40cm long x 14cm wide x 22cm high
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
